<div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">2013 film by Scott Cooper</div>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">Not to be confused with <a href="/wiki/Out_of_This_Furnace" title="Out of This Furnace">Out of This Furnace</a>.</div>
